            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-fe6bff40-d0d2-435e-9288-dfc7ade9b739">
                Mr. Deputy-Speaker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-fe6bff40-d0d2-435e-9288-dfc7ade9b739" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
