    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I apologise for interrupting the hon. Member, but I wish to understand his argument. Does he contend that in a democracy a minority of the country is entitled to fix the policy?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f6387367-241a-407f-b30d-7f8ad104161d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
