<p class="">No. I submit that the right hon. Gentleman, if he follows the logic of the right hon. Member for Epping (Mr. Churchill) is deprived of the right to use that argument, because if no General Election is to be held, who knows where the majority is?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a2d6e5c4-9b7a-45b6-aa81-81eab156adc3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
