<p class="">The answer is a simple one. I never said anything of the sort. If the hon. Member will read the book to which he has referred, he will see what is stated there.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6ea8920f-1f4f-4cd7-adc5-27ba4cca63b8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
