<p class="">I do not think the hon. Member will find anything in the OFFICIAL REPORT to show that my leader has run away from the possibilities or the probabilities of a General Election after the failure of the Government to carry out its pledges.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-82de2489-1af0-4679-aa39-fb36f3ca0bb3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
